ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of COLIN YOUNKER of North Wiltshire, Prince Edward Island, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Gerard J. Fitzpatrick whose term has expired.
